    Gastrointestinal Genome (UHGG) collection, comprising 204,938
    nonredundant genomes from 4,644 gut prokaryotes. These genomes
    encode {$>$}170 million protein sequences, which we collated in
    the Unified Human Gastrointestinal Protein (UHGP) catalog. The
